module:
   development.folder="dvlp">


    module, individual, product, relationship, structure, process plant













     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module to record:


the decomposition of an individual product into component individual products; 

the connections between individual products;

the individual products that are used to make a connection;

the relationship between an individual product and its container.






the existence of an individual product;



a whole-part relationship between two individual products;



a connection relationship between two individual products;



a containment relationship between two individual products;



the involvement of an individual product in a connection between
individual products.







structure of a class of product;
The structure of a class of product is within the
scope of the Class_of_product_structure application module.



the involvement of individual products, individual documents, individual of
people and individual organizations in an individual activity.
The involvement of individual products, individual
documents, individual people and individual organizations in an individual activity
is within the scope of the
Individual_involvement_in_activity application module.
